        <p>
            The <strong>"Sales Agents" section of the</strong> <strong>Movelys application is designed to manage agents or sales representatives who are paid on commission. It allows for organizing, tracking, and controlling information related to these external or internal partners, while ensuring transparency in the calculation and management of commissions.
        </p>
    </article>
