        <h3>3.2 Objectives of the Feature</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Centralize information related to sales agents.</li>
            <li>Track the performance and contacts of sales agents.</li>
            <li>Define a specific commission percentage for each individual.</li>
            <li>Provide advanced export and visualization tools.</li>
            <li>Facilitate HR and commercial management related to external sales.</li>
        </ul>
